    "category": "daily_encouragement",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 12
  },
  {
    "content": "学习最高效的方法：先理解，再记忆，最后练习。理解是一切的基础。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 13
  },
  {
    "content": "做错题不可怕，可怕的是同一道题错两次。整理错题本，是提分最快的方法。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 14
  },
  {
    "content": "番茄工作法：专注25分钟，休息5分钟。让大脑在专注和放松中高效切换。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 15
  },
  {
    "content": "费曼学习法：如果你能把一个知识点讲给别人听，说明你真正理解了。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 16
  },
  {
    "content": "先把课本上的例题吃透，比盲目刷题有效十倍。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 17
  },
  {
    "content": "学会给知识「编网」：把零散的知识点连成知识网络，记忆更牢固，应用更灵活。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 18
  },
  {
    "content": "复习的最佳时间点：学完当天、第三天、第七天、第十四天。间隔重复，事半功倍。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "study_method",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "normal",
    "display_order": 19
  },
  {
    "content": "你已经为这一天准备了很久，相信自己的积累，上考场只需正常发挥。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_7d",
    "display_order": 20
  },
  {
    "content": "考试是检验学习的手段，不是定义你的标签。放下包袱，轻装上阵。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_7d",
    "display_order": 21
  },
  {
    "content": "深呼吸，告诉自己：我准备好了。你比自己想象的更强大。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_7d",
    "display_order": 22
  },
  {
    "content": "考前最重要的事：吃好、睡好、心态好。知识已经在你脑子里了。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_7d",
    "display_order": 23
  },
  {
    "content": "稳住心态，先做会做的，再攻有把握的，最后试难的。一步一步来。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_7d",
    "display_order": 24
  },
  {
    "content": "紧张是正常的，适度紧张反而能帮你集中注意力。把紧张当作战斗力的一部分。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_30d",
    "display_order": 25
  },
  {
    "content": "不是只有你觉得压力大，每个正在拼搏的人都一样。但你选择了坚持，这就是你的勇气。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "pre_exam_motivation",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "pre_exam_30d",
    "display_order": 26
  },
  {
    "content": "累了就休息一下，但不要放弃。短暂的停歇是为了走更远的路。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 27
  },
  {
    "content": "觉得撑不住的时候，去操场跑两圈，或者听一首喜欢的歌。身体放松了，心情也会好起来。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 28
  },
  {
    "content": "偶尔考不好不代表什么，人生是长跑，一次摔倒不影响最终的方向。",
