    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 29
  },
  {
    "content": "焦虑来了不要逃避，写下让你焦虑的事，然后逐一解决。化焦虑为行动。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 30
  },
  {
    "content": "你不需要做到完美，只需要做到最好的自己。接受不完美，才能走得更远。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 31
  },
  {
    "content": "压力大的时候，试试5-4-3-2-1法：看5样东西、摸4样东西、听3种声音、闻2种气味、尝1种味道。让自己回到当下。",
    "author": null,
    "category": "stress_relief",
    "applicable_grades": ["gao1", "gao2", "gao3"],
    "applicable_phase": "all",
    "display_order": 32
  },
  {
